<div class="entrycontent">Sorry, can't play that file at work. I'll try looking later. <br /><br />It's generally not motorcyclists I have the issue with, it's SUVs and idiots in rich cars...but there have been a few idiot bikers acting like assholes and making me want to hit them. But not because I didn't see them. Let's face it--my car's tiny and low, how could I not see them?</div>

