<div class="entrycontent"><i>It has happend to me and frankly if I took him out I wouldn't have felt remorse over it.</i><br /><br />Sweet of you.<br /><br />Would you do it on purpose?  Would you open your car door into a bike riding down the breakdown lane in highway traffic?<br /><br />What about bicycles in the city?  Would you "take them out" too?  They're supposed to follow the rules of the road just like cars and motorcycles.</div>

